---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about CalcBuild — free online construction and home improvement calculators.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6">About CalcBuild</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        CalcBuild is a free online resource for construction and home improvement calculators. Our tools help homeowners, contractors, and DIY enthusiasts estimate materials, costs, and quantities for a wide range of projects.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We believe accurate estimates should be accessible to everyone. Whether you're planning a new driveway, re-roofing your house, or calculating materials for a landscaping project, our calculators provide instant, reliable results.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Accuracy</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        All our calculators use industry-standard formulas and material densities. Results include helpful tips and recommendations to ensure you order the right amount of materials for your project.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
